summary: This is an email requesting setup of a conference call line for the afternoon of October 22, 2019, to speak with an Epstein victim and her attorneys who are in different locations. It indicates coordination between legal parties and a victim.

events.title: Scheduled conference call with Epstein victim and attorneys
events.description: A conference call was scheduled for around 4pm to speak with an Epstein victim and her attorneys, who were all in different places.

keyFacts: An email dated October 22, 2019, requests setup of a conference call line for that afternoon.
The purpose of the call was to speak with an Epstein victim and her attorneys.
The victim and her attorneys were located in different places, necessitating a conference call.
